sub_title: LLM European Private Law | Legal Advisor @ Creative Clicks | Ex Non-profit Founder of INTERNaction
summary:
As an international student, who studied in Slovenia, UK and currently in the Netherlands, my interests lie in the field of private law. It ranges from company law, insolvency, property and commercial law to human rights. I also have a keen interest in PR. 

Recently I founded INTERNaction, which is a non-profit organization, aiming to secure legal human rights internships for university students, whilst providing media exposure to local NGOs across the globe.
